      • getGuildJson

        @Nullable
public static org.json.JSONObject getGuildJson​(java.lang.String guildId,
                                               boolean save)
        Reads guild json from file system from the corresponding guild.sbf file
        If that fails too it will try guildBase.sbf and after that guildBase.json from the Server data directory
